<node id="Dokumentenordner">
  <data key="d0">Dokumentenordner</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The **Dokumentenordner** refers to a structured digital folder system designed for organizing, storing, and managing documents within the Lizard platform. It serves as a repository for documents linked to specific equipment, operational resources, or assets, enabling efficient access and shared use across multiple Betriebsmittel (operational equipment or resources).

The Dokumentenordner functions as a centralized system for document organization, allowing users to categorize files by name, description, and public accessibility. It supports mass linking to equipment items, enabling documents to be associated with multiple Betriebsmittel simultaneously for streamlined access and collaboration. Within the Lizard Connect framework, Dokumentenordner can be structured to organize documents related to licenses or other asset categories, ensuring systematic storage and retrieval.

Additionally, the Dokumentenordner may include attributes such as a hierarchical folder structure, shared accessibility, and integration with operational workflows. Its primary purpose is to facilitate document management by providing a clear, organized, and scalable solution for linking and accessing documents tied to equipment or other system resources.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-028&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-051&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-019&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-052&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-063&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-064&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-054&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-055&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-006&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-059&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-038</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1781356261</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Betriebsmittel">
  <data key="d0">Betriebsmittel</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">**Betriebsmittel**

Betriebsmittel refers to equipment or assets managed within a system, encompassing both physical and digital items. These assets include tools, machinery, devices, and operational resources such as ladders or forklifts, which are tracked for inspection, maintenance, and compliance purposes. Betriebsmittel are often linked to identification systems like DynTags, QR-Codes, or NFC tags, enabling efficient management, inventory tracking, and operational referencing.

Within the Lizard platform and its associated systems (e.g., Lizard Pro, Lizard Connect), Betriebsmittel are central to workflows involving inspection orders, licensing, and collaboration. They may be assigned to specific locations, folders, or organizational structures, and their lifecycle—including inspection history and documentation—is systematically recorded. Betriebsmittel can also be shared with partners, constrained by license quotas, or managed under hierarchical relationships (e.g., parent-child structures). Additionally, they serve as digital twins, representing physical assets in a digital format for enhanced monitoring and operational control.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-028&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-039&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-007&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-050&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-061&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-008&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-018&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-051&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-062&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-041&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-019&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-052&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-031&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-063&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-010&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-042&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-020&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-053&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-032&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-064&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-025&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-043&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-021&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-054&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-065&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-012&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-002&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-022&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-055&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-066&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-013&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-045&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-003&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-035&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-067&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-046&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-024&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-057&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-015&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-047&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-005&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-026&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-037&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-016&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-048&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-006&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-027&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-059&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-038&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-049</data>
