<node id="Lizard">
  <data key="d0">Lizard</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">**Lizard** is a multifaceted software platform or system designed to centralize and streamline industrial safety, maintenance, compliance, and asset management processes. It serves as a comprehensive solution for managing operational equipment, inspections, and related workflows, integrating features such as dynamic tagging (DynTags), QR codes, NFC tags, and digital twins. The platform facilitates collaboration between operators and service providers, enabling data sharing, resource management, and secure communication through tools like ExpressImport and the LISS-Engine for intelligent data processing.

Lizard functions as a digital asset management system, tracking physical tools, equipment, and inspection results while ensuring data retention, attribute binding, and lifecycle documentation. It supports automated workflows, including data import, review processes, and security validations, with capabilities for token management, API integrations, and user administration for external auditors and developers. The system also incorporates AI-driven features for knowledge management, error handling, and manual correction, alongside hardware components like IIoT devices for real-time monitoring and compliance tracking. Additionally, Lizard provides functionalities for managing inspection orders, technician workflows, licensing, and compliance data, often serving as a target system for batch imports and live inventory transfers.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-028&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-039&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-007&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-029&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-061&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-051&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-062&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-030&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-041&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-009&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-019&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-052&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-031&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-063&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-010&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-042&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-053&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-032&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-064&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-025&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-011&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-043&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-021&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-054&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-065&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-012&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-044&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-002&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-022&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-055&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-034&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-066&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-013&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-04