<node id="Prüfergebnisse">
  <data key="d0">Prüfergebnisse</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">**Prüfergebnisse**

Prüfergebnisse refers to inspection results, findings, or certificates associated with operational equipment, assets, or inventory items, serving as a comprehensive system for recording, managing, and verifying compliance. These results are extracted from unstructured data sources, such as TÜV reports, and are systematically stored in databases like the Lizard system, where they can be linked to Dyntag IDs during import processes. The Prüfergebnisse encompasses various inspection outcomes, including manufacturer certificates, initial inspections, and test data, which may be attached to assets or items during dispatch or import to confirm adherence to regulatory or operational standards.

Functionally, Prüfergebnisse serves as both a resource and an overview system within organizational workflows, enabling users to view, manage, and generate reports on conducted inspections. It includes detailed records such as asset identifiers, inspection categories, status updates, owner information, comments, and inspection protocols, providing a centralized repository for compliance verification and operational oversight. Additionally, Prüfergebnisse may include possible outcomes of inspection processes, further supporting decision-making and regulatory documentation.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-028&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-039&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-050&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-061&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-040&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-031&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-025&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-043&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-012&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-044&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-035&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-047&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-026&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-059</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1781356261</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
