<node id="DynTag">
  <data key="d0">DynTag</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">**DynTag** is a dynamic tagging system designed for linking physical assets or items to digital resources, primarily through scannable QR codes or NFC tags. These tags contain a unique address (e.g., `dyntag.link/AbC123XYz`) that redirects users to specific profiles, item pages, or resources, often with appended paths or query parameters for deeper navigation (e.g., `https://dyntag.link/AbC123XYz/dokumente`). The system supports both Lizard Connect item pages and third-party integrations, functioning as a bridge between physical tags and digital data.

The tags are dynamic, allowing targets to be reconfigured without reprinting, and incorporate features like Path-Forwarding, scan logging, and lifecycle management (reservation, connection, activation, and disconnection). They are used for asset identification, tracking, and operational equipment categorization, with applications ranging from inspections to tool management. DynTags employ a 10-digit Short-ID or alphanumeric codes (including special characters like `+` or `-`) to avoid URL conflicts, offering a robust alternative to longer UUIDs. The system is compatible with NFC and QR scanning methods, enabling seamless integration with digital workflows in the Lizard ecosystem.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-028&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-007&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-017&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-061&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-008&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-052&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-063&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-032&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-054&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-002&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-055&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-034&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-013&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-015&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-005&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-037&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-016&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-059</data>
