<node id="Prüfauftrag">
  <data key="d0">Prüfauftrag</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The **Prüfauftrag** (German for "inspection order") is a standardized task or order designed to document, assign, and manage inspection-related activities for operational equipment, referred to as *Betriebsmittel*. It serves as a formal framework for scheduling, resource allocation, and execution, ensuring compliance and safety through structured verification processes. The Prüfauftrag is typically created and managed within digital platforms such as the **Lizard** system or the **Einsatzplaner**, where it is assigned to technicians, partners, or operational resources. Key functionalities include tracking working time via the **Zeiterfassung** system for billing and productivity analysis, documenting inspection intervals, and associating checklists, photos, and results with specific equipment items.

The Prüfauftrag functions as a digital folder consolidating all necessary information for a technician’s workday or project, including scheduling details, employee assignments, and equipment tracking. It can be tailored to various contexts, such as ongoing orders within a tenant for a specific customer, tasks assigned to partners for execution, or verification tasks referenced in time-tracking systems with unique identifiers and partner-specific data. The order may also include role-based access controls to define framework conditions and resources, while its flexible structure allows for the addition of documents, status changes, or direct asset management during on-site inspections. Additionally, the Prüfauftrag serves as a filterable criterion in data displays and can be compiled into a compilation of items to be inspected by a designated inspector on a specified date.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-028&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-007&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-050&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-061&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-018&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-051&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-062&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-052&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-063&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-010&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-042&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-032&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-021&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-065&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-012&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-002&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-022&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-034&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-066&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-003&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-035&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-004&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-024&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-047&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-026&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-037&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-006&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-038&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-036</data>
