<node id="Zusammenarbeit">
  <data key="d0">Zusammenarbeit</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">**Zusammenarbeit** refers to a multifaceted collaboration framework within a system, encompassing various forms of partnerships, shared access, and operational integrations between entities such as companies, service providers, customers, and operators. It serves as both a functional module and a contextual attribute, enabling the management, tracking, and filtering of collaborative relationships tied to equipment, assets, or operational processes.

At its core, *Zusammenarbeit* functions as a collaboration entity or module within the system, facilitating partnerships through structured fields such as name, partner details, address, and internal notes. It supports shared access to operational equipment (*Betriebsmittel*), allowing external partners or service providers to interact with specific areas or assets while maintaining controlled permissions. This shared access is further enabled through digital collaboration frameworks, including shared folders or filtered attributes, which streamline data display and categorization for inspections, asset management, or internal reference.

Additionally, *Zusammenarbeit* acts as a contextual attribute or filter, enabling users to categorize, manage, or retrieve items based on collaboration-related parameters. It may indicate whether equipment is shared with a partner or serve as a prerequisite for certain system functionalities, such as confirmed customer collaborations. The framework is designed to integrate seamlessly with partner records, operational workflows, and digital platforms like Lizard Connect, ensuring cohesive management of partnerships across multiple use cases.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-028&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-060&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-061&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-062&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-052&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-025&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-043&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-054&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-065&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-012&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-055&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-066&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-003&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-004&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-047&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-005&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-026&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-059</data>
