<node id="Firma">
  <data key="d0">Firma</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The term **Firma** refers to a company or organization entity within the system, serving as a central identifier for various operational, administrative, and collaborative functions.

Across different system interfaces and records, **Firma** is consistently represented as a company name or identifier used for tracking, invoicing, and resource management. It appears in partner records to facilitate collaboration and financial processes, such as invoicing and token removal in the token management interface. Additionally, **Firma** is integrated into operational workflows, including equipment forms and company settings, where it serves as a field for company identification on reports and documents. In usage metrics, **Firma** is recognized as the primary entity consuming system resources, ensuring accountability and resource allocation. The term may also distinguish itself from related fields, such as *Firmenname*, in certain forms, indicating a structured approach to company data representation. Overall, **Firma** functions as a foundational entity for managing company-specific data, interactions, and resource utilization within the system.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-028&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-060&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-062&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-043&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-003&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-015&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-058&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-016</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1781356265</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Service">
  <data key="d0">Service</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The **Service** entity within the system encompasses multiple functionalities and modules, primarily centered around service-related operations, partner license management, time tracking, and inspection processes.

It includes a dedicated section for evaluating time bookings under "Service &gt; Zeiterfassung," as well as a module for partner license management and time tracking within the Lizard platform. Additionally, the **Service** module manages inspection templates, ensuring standardized procedures for examinations and inspections. The entity also facilitates backend services, such as redirecting DynTags and retrieving data, while integrating administrative features like Partnerlizenzverwaltung (partner license management) in Lizard Connect.

Furthermore, **Service** serves as an organizational or software service offering broader functionalities, including inspection orders, examination processes, and templates for inspections and collaborations. These components collectively define **Service** as a multifaceted system module supporting service operations, administrative tasks, and inspection workflows.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-060&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-020&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-054&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-034&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-003&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-023&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-026&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-049</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1781356265</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Prüfvorlagen">
  <data key="d0">Prüfvorlagen</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">**Prüfvorlagen** are standardized templates used to define inspection criteria, procedures, and standards for various types of equipment, ensuring consistency and compliance in inspection processes. These templates are managed within the Service module and serve as a foundational resource for creating and standardizing new inspection workflows. They encompass fields such as names, applicable norms or guidelines, and structured question catalogs to guide technicians during inspections.

Prüfvorlagen are specifically designed for recurring inspections and tests of operating equipment, outlining detailed procedures, required documentation, and checklist items to ensure thorough and repeatable evaluations. They may include predefined intervals for inspections, which can vary depending on the equipment type or regulatory requirements. Additionally, these templates provide a framework for inspections by specifying applicable standards and the key questions technicians must address during assessments.

Within the Lizard system, Prüfvorlagen are categorized as a dedicated resource for managing standardized inspection templates, facilitating centralized control and accessibility. Their primary purpose is to streamline inspection processes, reduce variability, and ensure adherence to established norms and operational guidelines.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-060&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-052&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-023&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-067&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-026&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-006&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-059&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-049&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-036</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1781356265</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Zu importierende Dateien">
  <data key="d0">Zu importierende Dateien</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Files allowed for upload during the import process, restricted to PDF, XLS, and XLSX formats.&lt;SEP&gt;File upload field for importing data into the system, supporting formats like PDF and XLS.</data>
