  <data key="d2">Text editor field for adding rich content to the inspection item.&lt;SEP&gt;The actual text content of a report, which may include placeholders for dynamic data&lt;SEP&gt;Configuration of result logic in JSON/XML format</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-039&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-050&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-060</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
