  <data key="d0">CSV-Import</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">A process for creating operational equipment items from a CSV list with individual values per row and transferring them to Lizard.&lt;SEP&gt;A feature enabling the import of data from CSV files into the system.&lt;SEP&gt;Process for importing data from CSV files into the system&lt;SEP&gt;A process for generating items from a CSV list with individual values per row.&lt;SEP&gt;A process for creating items from a CSV list with individual values per row&lt;SEP&gt;A method to import values per position from a CSV list, including Dyntag columns</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-039&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-040&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-019&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-035&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-014&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-058</data>
