  <data key="d0">Speicher</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Storage space managed within the system, which can become cluttered without proper workflows.&lt;SEP&gt;Storage resources managed within the system, including an overview of sent catalogs and cleanup options&lt;SEP&gt;Storage space within a browser, whose quota may need to be checked or adjusted when full.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-039&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-043&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-016</data>
