<node id="Name">
  <data key="d0">Name</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The term **Name** refers to a textual designation or identifier used across various entities and systems to represent, categorize, or label items, templates, or results. In the context of Betriebsmittel (equipment or assets), it serves as an internal identifier stored as a text field, facilitating machine readability and import processes (e.g., `leiter_laenge`). Similarly, it functions as a title or designation for Textvorlagen (text templates), inspection-related entries, and Dokumentenordner (document folders), ensuring consistent identification and organization.

Additionally, **Name** is employed as a field for inspection results (e.g., "Mangelhaft mit Weiterbetrieb") and catalog categories, where it aids in internal identification and visibility. It may also represent the title of an inspection template or a category/item identifier, depending on the system's context. The versatility of **Name** underscores its role as a foundational attribute for tracking, referencing, and managing diverse data entries within operational and inspection workflows.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-060&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-050&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-051&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-025&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-043&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-033&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-055&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-003&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-049</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1781356268</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
