<node id="Standort">
  <data key="d0">Standort</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">**Standort**

Standort refers to a physical or geographic location associated with items, equipment (Betriebsmittel), or operational resources. It encompasses address components such as street, postal code, city, and country, serving as a structured data attribute in systems like Stammdaten and Lizard master data. Standort can represent hierarchical structures, including buildings, vehicles, or sub-locations, and is used for organizing, tracking, and managing assets, inspections, or operational tasks.

In practical applications, Standort functions as a mandatory or optional field in catalogs, asset management systems, and location management tools. It may be filtered, renamed, or deleted (if no items are attached) and can serve as a default location for catalog positions. Standort is also referenced in data displays, filtering mechanisms, and hierarchical organization within settings, such as in location management systems under "Standorte." Additionally, it may include digital locations in some contexts, though its primary focus remains on physical or geographic contexts.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-060&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-061&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-008&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-051&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-062&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-009&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-031&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-063&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-032&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-064&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-025&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-043&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-021&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-054&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-055&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-034&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-066&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-046&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-057&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-047&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-026&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-037&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-036</data>
