<node id="Kategorie">
  <data key="d0">Kategorie</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">**Kategorie** is a multifaceted classification and grouping system used across various contexts within an organizational framework, primarily centered on asset management, inventory systems, and operational workflows. It serves as a structured mechanism for defining attributes, organizing items, and standardizing processes.

In the context of **inventory systems**, *Kategorie* functions as a field that determines the attribute set for items, such as those categorized under "Lizard-Kategorie" or general inventory categories like "Lager" (storage) and "Fuhrpark" (fleet). It may also act as a mandatory field that categorizes the type of item or resource, ensuring consistency in data management. Additionally, *Kategorie* serves as an internal grouping mechanism for organizing assets, such as "Betriebsmittel" (operational equipment), where it defines classifications like fire extinguishers or other functional types. These classifications can be predefined or user-defined, enabling the assignment of specific attributes and inspection templates tailored to the equipment type.

Within **text templates (Textvorlagen)**, *Kategorie* defines the use case of a template, such as for defects or emails, ensuring that the appropriate template is applied based on the classification. It also functions as a structured blueprint for organizing items, linking to broader catalog systems to determine available attributes and classifications. In this capacity, *Kategorie* supports actions such as viewing, editing, deleting, duplicating, or exporting, acting as a foundational element for asset management and operational workflows.

Furthermore, *Kategorie* plays a role in **task order hierarchies**, where it may represent an upper category, such as maintenance or inspection, providing a high-level classification for organizing and tracking tasks. It can also group inspection results, such as "Sichtprüfung" (visual inspection), facilitating structured data aggregation and analysis. Overall, *Kategorie* is a versatile classification system that ensures consistency, standardization, and efficiency across multiple domains within an organization.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-060&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-039&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-050&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-008&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-051&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-031&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-032&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-025&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-043&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-021&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-065&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-055&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-003&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-046&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-037</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
