<node id="Prüfergebnis">
  <data key="d0">Prüfergebnis</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">**Prüfergebnis** refers to the documented outcome of an inspection or examination, encompassing various formats and contexts within a system or workflow. It serves as a comprehensive record of findings, validation outcomes, or proof documents associated with items, equipment, or catalog entries.

In its most general form, a **Prüfergebnis** represents the result of an inspection, including detailed findings and any attached media such as works certificates or initial inspection reports. These results can be documented in multiple formats, including PDF reports generated after an inspection, which may feature configurable templates, content sections, and optional time tracking. The inspection results may also be presented as part of a PDF report’s configurable section, tailored to specific layout requirements.

Within a catalog or system, **Prüfergebnis** includes structured data such as the title, last inspection date, inspection interval, examiner details, and comments. These results are often managed in a dedicated verification section, where inspection reports or validation outcomes are uploaded and associated with catalog items. The system allows for the archiving of older inspection results to maintain a clean and organized overview. Additionally, **Prüfergebnis** can be exported as a ZIP file containing detailed reports of performed checks, ensuring comprehensive documentation and accessibility.

Overall, **Prüfergebnis** functions as a critical component in tracking, validating, and archiving inspection outcomes, supporting transparency and compliance in equipment or item management.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-039&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-062&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-030&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-063&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-011&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-034&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-014&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-057&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-015&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-058&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-048&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-027</data>
