<node id="Zeiterfassung">
  <data key="d0">Zeiterfassung</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">**Zeiterfassung** is a comprehensive time-tracking system designed to record, evaluate, and manage working hours associated with inspection orders and partner license management. It serves as a critical tool for cost accounting, customer billing, and operational transparency within the Lizard platform and its associated applications.

The system enables employees to start, stop, and document time intervals directly linked to inspection orders, either through the Lizard app or web interface. Recorded time data can be manually adjusted if necessary and included in PDF inspection reports to ensure customer transparency. Additionally, Zeiterfassung supports detailed time evaluation, allowing filtering by time period and tester for precise analysis. A summary of recorded times, such as total duration, can optionally be displayed in generated PDF reports.

Beyond inspection tasks, Zeiterfassung also facilitates time tracking for service providers managing partner licenses and external access. It is integrated into the Lizard platform as a dedicated module under Partnerlizenzverwaltung, accessible via the Seitenleiste in Lizard Connect under the Service section. The system can be initiated automatically when starting an inspection order, ensuring seamless integration into workflows. Overall, Zeiterfassung enhances efficiency, accountability, and billing accuracy for inspection-related and partner management activities.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-039&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-020&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-011&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-021&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-054&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-002&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-003&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-035&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-047&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-058&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-048&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-038&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-049&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-036</data>
