<node id="Item">
  <data key="d0">Item</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The **Item** entity refers to a record or entry in the system, typically representing a piece of equipment, asset, or operational resource being managed. It serves as a generic term for entries such as catalog items, devices, tools, or inspection tasks, functioning as a digital twin of physical equipment or assets within the Lizard system. Items are created and managed digitally, often associated with attributes, codes, and documentation like proof documents or inspection data.

Within the Lizard platform, Items are operational assets or equipment that undergo processes such as activation, archiving, and inspection. They can be cataloged, scanned, or transmitted, with references in configurations like Prüfergebnis steps. Synonymous with *Betriebsmittel* (operational equipment), Items are central to inventory management, enabling tracking and digital representation of physical resources. Each Item may include Dyntag IDs and attached files, serving as a structured entity for system-wide resource management.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-039&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-052&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-031&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-063&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-043&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-054&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-012&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-044&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-055&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-056&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-014&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-046&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-057&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-015&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-058</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1781356271</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
