<node id="Dyntag">
  <data key="d0">Dyntag</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Dyntag refers to a dynamic tagging system or physical tag used for identification, tracking, and linking purposes across various contexts, including equipment, assets, documents, and inventory systems.

In its physical form, Dyntag is a tag—often embedded with a short ID or QR code—assigned to equipment or assets for identification and tracking. These tags facilitate automated tracking and verification by linking QR codes to specific positions or items within a system. The short ID or QR code serves as a unique identifier, enabling the linking of items to external resources, inventory records, or inspection workflows. Dyntag may also appear as a speaking column name in Excel, representing a dynamic tag associated with asset catalog fields.

Beyond physical tags, Dyntag functions as a dynamic tagging system that categorizes and organizes documents, equipment, and inventory items. It supports linking items to identifiers via URLs or codes, streamlining tracking and management processes. Additionally, Dyntag can be integrated into platforms or systems that assign IDs to positions, which may then be linked to items during import or workflow processes. Optional tags or URLs may also be associated with equipment records for enhanced flexibility.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-039&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-040&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-062&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-009&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-031&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-020&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-011&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-043&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-012&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-044&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-035&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-014&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-047&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-058&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-048</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1781356271</data>
