<node id="QR-Code">
  <data key="d0">QR-Code</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The QR-Code is a type of DynTag represented as a two-dimensional barcode designed for machine readability and efficient scanning via smartphone cameras. It serves multiple purposes, primarily acting as a scannable code to access the öffentliche (public) URL of an Item or to link Dyntags to specific assets within the Lizard system. The QR-Code functions as a machine-readable optical label, often containing a Dyntag ID or other encoded data, enabling automated tracking, asset identification, and access to equipment information—either online or offline through cached data.

The QR-Code is characterized by its robustness, reliability, and adaptability, making it suitable for printing on various surfaces, including industrial stickers for asset identification. It is widely used in inspections, where it facilitates the scanning of equipment tags, and in document access, allowing public retrieval without login credentials. Supported by Lizard Connect, the QR-Code is a matrix barcode technology that stores information for quick access, including foreign manufacturer codes that can be adopted by Lizard. Its design prioritizes clarity, cleanliness, and visibility to ensure reliable scanning.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-039&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-007&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-061&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-008&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-062&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-041&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-009&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-031&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-063&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-020&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-054&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-044&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-002&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-022&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-034&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-014&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-057&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-047&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-037&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-048&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-027</data>
