<node id="Lizard Connect">
  <data key="d0">Lizard Connect</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">**Lizard Connect** is a multi-platform software system designed to facilitate equipment inspection workflows, asset management, and digital-physical asset linking through advanced connectivity and scanning technologies. It serves as a mobile application available for both iOS and Android, enabling users to quickly identify and connect physical assets—such as equipment or devices—with their corresponding digital records using multiple identification methods. These include Near Field Communication (NFC), QR codes, and Bluetooth, providing flexibility in how assets are scanned and accessed.

The system integrates with external NFC scanners and supports Bluetooth connectivity, allowing seamless interaction with compatible devices, including LizardPro hardware. Lizard Connect functions as a central interface for operators, service providers, and administrators, offering tools to manage and monitor equipment, documents, licenses, and inspection workflows. It also facilitates the retrieval of equipment details in a view mode, supporting scanning of tags and identifiers to access relevant data.

Additionally, Lizard Connect is designed to work in conjunction with external services such as the DynTag-Service, enhancing its capability to manage and track equipment across various operational contexts. The platform emphasizes efficiency in asset identification, linking, and inspection management, positioning itself as a comprehensive solution for digital asset integration and equipment oversight.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-007&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-017&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-008&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-018&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-041&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-042&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-020&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-032&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-054&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-022&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-015&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-037</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1781356273</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
