  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">An inspection category standard under German occupational safety regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Inspection category or standard related to electrical safety regulations in Germany.&lt;SEP&gt;German occupational safety regulation standard for electrical inspections.&lt;SEP&gt;German occupational safety regulation (Unfallverhütungsvorschrift) related to electrical safety inspections.&lt;SEP&gt;A German regulation (Unfallverhütungsvorschrift) related to occupational safety and equipment inspection.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulatory standard for electrical safety inspections in Germany.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-040&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-023&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-024&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-037</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
