</node>
<node id="Prüfkategorie">
  <data key="d0">Prüfkategorie</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The **Prüfkategorie** is a classification system used to categorize and manage inspections based on the type of equipment or asset involved. It serves as a dynamic attribute selector, determining the appropriate input mask, checklists, and applicable standards for inspections. The category is selected by users to define the scope of an inspection, such as "Electrical Devices" (Elektrische Geräte), "Ladders," or "Electrical Tools," ensuring that the correct procedures and norms are applied.

In the context of **Betriebsmittel** (operational equipment), the Prüfkategorie specifies the type of inspection required, such as recurring inspections or technical classifications for equipment like "Anschlagkette" (lifting chains) or "Elektrogerät" (electrical devices). It functions as a filter criterion in data displays, enabling users to group and categorize inspection norms, standards, or assets efficiently. Within systems like **Lizard Connect** or **Prüfauftrag**, the Prüfkategorie acts as a technical classification attribute, streamlining the assignment of checklists and compliance requirements based on predefined categories.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-061&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-008&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-040&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-009&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-025&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-043&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-054&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-055&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-034&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-023&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-024&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-047&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-026&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-027&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-049</data>
