<node id="Eigentümer">
  <data key="d0">Eigentümer</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The term **Eigentümer** refers to an individual or entity with ownership rights over specific assets, resources, or items within a system, primarily used as a filter criterion in data display.

In the context of equipment or resources, an **Eigentümer** is defined as the owner or partner company associated with *Betriebsmittel* (operational equipment or resources), stored as a text field to identify responsible individuals or entities. This role encompasses ownership rights over assets or licenses, such as those managed in *Lizard Connect*, where the **Eigentümer** may perform actions like archiving or deletion. Additionally, the term serves as a filter to identify the owner of items, enabling users to refine data displays based on ownership status.

The **Eigentümer** may also apply to *Dokumentenordner* (document folders), where the owner or responsible party holds authority over administrative tasks. Across these contexts, the **Eigentümer** functions as a key criterion for filtering, ensuring clarity in ownership attribution within the system.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-061&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-051&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-062&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-043&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-054&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-055&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-034&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-047</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1781356275</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
