<node id="Verantwortlicher">
  <data key="d0">Verantwortlicher</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">**Verantwortlicher**

The *Verantwortlicher* refers to an individual assigned responsibility for managing, overseeing, or inspecting operational assets, resources, or tasks. This role serves as a filter criterion in data displays, enabling the assignment of accountability for specific items such as *Betriebsmittel* (operational equipment or assets) within systems like Lizard Connect. The *Verantwortlicher* may function as an owner, manager, or inspector, ensuring proper oversight of assets, licenses, or related operational activities.

The term encompasses a broad scope, including employees responsible for managing *Betriebsmittel*, individuals overseeing inspections, and those assigned to manage or oversee specific operational resources or tasks. In some contexts, the *Verantwortlicher* is stored as a text field, allowing flexibility in recording the responsible person’s name or role. The role emphasizes accountability, enabling targeted filtering and assignment of responsibility within organizational workflows.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-061&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-008&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-051&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-062&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-063&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-064&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-025&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-043&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-054&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-055&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-034&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-047</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1781356275</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Items">
  <data key="d0">Items</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Items refer to individual entries or records within catalogs, representing specific equipment or inventory items. These entries are assets or resources managed by users, including equipment and documents, and are linked to responsible employees within the system. Items are operational assets or equipment managed in the system, referenced in roles and qualifications within the Lizard platform.

They are individual entries managed separately per company, created from CSV data in the catalog, and selected for batch upload. Items can also be part of a collection of equipment or assets being managed in the system, appearing as individual records or files within a batch for processing. Additionally, Items may be equipment items selected for inspection or document folder linking, encompassing all individual entries or records managed within the system, such as equipment or documents.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-008&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-040&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-019&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-052&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-064&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-025&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-011&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-023&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-004&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-005&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-016</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1781356276</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
