<node id="LISS-Engine">
  <data key="d0">LISS-Engine</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The **LISS-Engine** (Lizard Intelligent Scanning System) is a core technological platform developed by LISS, designed to automate administrative tasks by integrating Large Language Models (LLMs) with specialized database logic. It serves as an intelligent intermediary between raw data and the Lizard database, enabling automated workflows for equipment management, inspections, and file processing.

The system functions as both a backend processor and an AI-powered engine, handling uploaded files to perform automated analysis, data extraction, and cleansing. Its multi-stage memory system allows it to adapt to company-specific requirements, facilitating mass data onboarding through structured formats like Excel lists and PDF reports. Specifically, the LISS-Engine automates the reading, structuring, and importing of data from these formats, streamlining processes such as the mass-import of *Betriebsmittel* (operational equipment or resources). Additionally, it enhances operational efficiency by reducing manual intervention in administrative tasks.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-040&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-042&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-020&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-012&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-013&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-014&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-004&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-057</data>
  <data key="d4">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1781356277</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
