<edge source="Betriebsmittel" target="Lizard">
  <data key="d7">14.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation **(Betriebsmittel, Lizard)** describes how the Lizard platform interacts with *Betriebsmittel*—a German term typically referring to operational equipment, assets, or resources used in industrial, maintenance, or inspection contexts.

Lizard serves as a centralized digital system for managing, tracking, and overseeing the lifecycle of *Betriebsmittel*, functioning as a "digital memory" that ensures compliance, safety, and operational efficiency. Within the platform, *Betriebsmittel* are represented as digital twins, enabling real-time monitoring, status updates, and lifecycle management. The system assigns unique tags to *Betriebsmittel* for identification and operational tracking, integrating them into inspection orders to streamline workflows. Lizard autonomously manages equipment statuses, resetting them to *"Nicht geprüft"* (not inspected) upon archiving all inspection results, ensuring traceability and adherence to regulatory standards.

Additionally, Lizard maintains an inventory of physical assets, linking them to digital records for inventory control and operational oversight. The platform consolidates these functions—equipment tracking, digital twin representation, tagging, and lifecycle management—into a unified system designed to enhance maintenance, compliance, and asset utilization.</data>
  <data key="d9">assigns,associates with,automatic correction,contains,digital twin management,includes,links to,managed in,manages,status management,tracks</data>
  <data key="d10">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-028&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-007&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-061&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-041&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-052&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-032&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-022&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-066&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-045&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-035&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-024&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-026&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-006&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-059</data>
  <data key="d11">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1781356282</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
