<edge source="Betriebsmittel" target="Prüfauftrag">
  <data key="d7">11.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation **(Betriebsmittel, Prüfauftrag)** describes the connection between operational equipment (Betriebsmittel) and inspection orders (Prüfauftrag) in a systematic verification process.

In this relationship, **Betriebsmittel**—which refers to operational equipment, assets, or machinery—are systematically associated with **Prüfaufträge**, which are inspection orders or tasks. These orders are assigned to specific equipment to ensure compliance, condition assessment, or systematic verification. The Prüfauftrag serves as a compilation or management tool that includes and organizes the Betriebsmittel requiring inspection, ensuring that all relevant assets are accounted for during the process.

The relation emphasizes a bidirectional association: Betriebsmittel are added to or included in Prüfaufträge, while inspection orders are explicitly assigned to operational equipment for task execution. This ensures that inspections are structured, traceable, and aligned with regulatory or operational requirements. The primary purpose is to facilitate compliance checks, maintenance, and condition monitoring of equipment within an operational framework.</data>
  <data key="d9">added to,assessment,assigned to,associated,contains,included in,includes,inspected,inspection,inspection compilation,inspects,manages,subject to</data>
  <data key="d10">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-028&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-061&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-018&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-051&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-052&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-063&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-032&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-065&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-012&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-024&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-037</data>
  <data key="d11">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1781356284</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Betriebsmittel" target="DynTag">
  <data key="d7">8.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation **(Betriebsmittel, DynTag)** describes the connection between *Betriebsmittel* (assets or operational equipment) and *DynTags* (dynamic identification tags), facilitating tracking, scanning, and digital identification.

In this relationship, *DynTags* serve as QR or NFC tags physically attached to *Betriebsmittel* to enable identification during inspections, operational tracking, or digital scanning. The tags are linked to *Betriebsmittel* profiles, which contain relevant paths and parameters for system integration. This linkage allows the retrieval of detailed equipment information when scanned, supporting physical tracking and operational monitoring. *DynTags* are assigned to assets within the system, ensuring that each *Betriebsmittel* can be uniquely identified and managed digitally. The relationship emphasizes the role of *DynTags* in bridging physical equipment with digital systems for efficient asset management.</data>
  <data key="d9">affixed to,assigned to,association,equipment management,identification tag,identified by,identifies,linked to,tag association</data>
  <data key="d10">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-028&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-061&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-052&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-032&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-002&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-013&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-015&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-037</data>
  <data key="d11">LizardDocu.md</data>
  <data key="d12">1781356286</data>
