<edge source="Betriebsmittel" target="Standort">
  <data key="d7">11.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation **(Betriebsmittel, Standort)** describes the association between assets (Betriebsmittel) and their locations (Standort), emphasizing tracking, management, and inventory purposes.

In this relationship, a Standort serves as a designated place where Betriebsmittel are stored, assigned, or used, enabling systematic oversight for inventory, inspection, and operational access. Betriebsmittel are linked to a specific Standort to indicate their physical or logical placement, ensuring clear reference for management and reference. The Standort field functions as a tracking mechanism, recording where equipment is stored or utilized, which supports logistical coordination and resource allocation. Additionally, the association facilitates partner access by hosting Betriebsmittel at designated locations, aligning with inventory and operational workflows. The relationship underscores that each Betriebsmittel is either directly located at a Standort or assigned to one, reinforcing its role in structured asset management.</data>
  <data key="d9">assigned to,assigns,associated with,association,attribute,context,has location,hosts,located at,location,organizes,tracking</data>
  <data key="d10">doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-051&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-062&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-063&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-032&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-064&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-025&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-043&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-021&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-066&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-057&lt;SEP&gt;doc-fb57212021fb1e5e7a76ae882be19321-chunk-037</data>
  <data key="d11">LizardDocu.md</data>
